{
  "arquivo": "ca03_05",
  "total": 194,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Oooohh!\\nThis gate looks very Okinawan!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I've seen this torii gate on TV before.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "That's Shureimon.\\nIt's a famous building in Okinawa,\\nso it's often featured in the media.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "There's a plaque on top of the gate,\\nis that how 'shurei' is read?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "That's read as 'shurei no kuni,'\\nmeaning to uphold etiquette.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Oh, I see.\\nYou really know your stuff, Fu-kun.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "When you find places you've known about but\\nnever been to like this one, it really makes you feel like\\nyou're in Okinawa and it's very exciting!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Hey, before we go in,\\nshould we all take a photo together?\\nA commemorative photo of our first Okinawa sightseeing.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, we should definitely hit up more of these famous spots much like this one.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "A picture...with Futaro...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Miku?\\nWe're gonna take a picture, c'mere.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "HYAAH?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Woah?!\\nSorry, did I startle you?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I-I wanna take a picture with Raiha-chan!\\nNino! Take it!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Okay, okay.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Whaaa! Miku, you're so sneaky!\\nI want to take a picture with Raiha-chan, too!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Alright, Raiha-chan will be in the center, then.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Well aren't you just so popular, Raiha-chan.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Ehehe.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I'm gonna take a picture.\\nAlright, say cheese.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Both",
      "texto_en": "Cheeeeese!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Ch-cheese.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Umm.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Alright, now let's take a group photo!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Who's gonna take the picture if everyone's gonna be in the photo?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Okay, I will.\\nI'll take one, then someone else can take the next one.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Alright, line up, line up.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Hm?\\nMiku, you don't need to be next to Uesugi-san?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "HUH?!\\nI-It's fine!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Big bro, you need to be more attentive.\\nYou should be standing next to her at times like these.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, but...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Okay! This is good enough!\\nIchika, take it quickly!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Okay.\\nAlright then, here we go.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Wait, let me take it!\\nIchika, come line up!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Kay, thanks.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Miku, are you alright?\\nShall I take the picture?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "No don't worry about it. Everyone get ready.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Right-o.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "!...\\nFutaro, look this way!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "~~~~~!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Miku? What's wrong?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "S-sorry! I'll take it now!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Alright! I took it! Now, let's keep moving!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Wait, what?\\nMiku, there's no need to rush.\\nWe have time, you know?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Miku-saaan! Wait!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(What the heck is going on, what's up with Miku...?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Fu-kun, you too, let's go.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Y-yeah.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Ichika, this is...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "We have no choice but to ask Futaro-kun, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Miku, are you okay?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I think...I'm okay...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "It's cause you tried to run when you don't even have stamina.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Shurijo Castle has a surprising amount\\nof elevation changes.\\nLet's take it easy.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "O-okay...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "This torii gate is amazing!\\nIt looks so durable!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "This is Zuisenmon.\\nIt means 'auspicious spring.'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Wow!\\nYotsuba-san, you're so knowledgeable!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Hehehe, you're making me blush.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Yotsuba, your brochure is sticking out of your pocket.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "AAGH?!\\nDon't expose me like that, Nino!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Teehee.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(She's laughing. Miku seems like her usual self now,\\n but earlier, she was definitely acting strange.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Futaro-kun, can I talk to you for a second?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hm? What is it?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "It's about Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Hmm? It looks like you don't want to be asked about something.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's not like that...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Futaro-kun,\\ndid you do something to upset Miku?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "WHA%p-2;――%p;?!\\nWhat do you mean, upset her?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Like, you did something to bother her,\\nor something like that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 75,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Since coming to Okinawa, Miku has been acting strange.\\nI think she's avoiding you...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 76,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 77,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "I'm right, aren't I?\\nCould it be that you unintentionally\\nmade her upset?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 78,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Uesugi-kun?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 79,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, that's not true! That's a false accusation!\\nI do feel like I'm being avoided,\\nbut I can't think of any reason why!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 80,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Really now?\\nKnowing you,\\ncould it be that you did something unconsciously?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 81,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Well, a girl's heart is delicate, you know?\\nEven the smallest things can hurt a girl's feelings.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 82,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Anyway, I have no idea what it could be about.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 83,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Alright fine. For now, I'll trust your words.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 84,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Wowww, it's so pretty!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 85,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "This is really amazing....",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 86,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Yes, I didn't expect it to be this beautiful.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 87,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "We can go inside, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 88,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, we can.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 89,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "The building in front of us is the main hall, and the\\nbuildings on the left and right are the south and\\nnorth halls, with an exhibition room inside too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 90,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Wow, it looks very impressive.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 91,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Then, why don't we all just explore freely for a while?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 92,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Sounds good. Let's meet back here when we're finished.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 93,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Okay, in that case, I'll stick with Miku...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 94,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Well, I'll go in and take a look.\\nRaiha-chan, do you want to come too?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 95,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, I wanna go too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 96,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "I think I'll take a walk for a little longer.\\nI want to take in this beautiful scenery. See ya.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 97,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 98,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Um, Futa%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 99,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Miku.\\nYou wanna go with me to%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 100,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "HYAA?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 101,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ah...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 102,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "She ran away again.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 103,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Nino, Yotsuba...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 104,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Excuse me, Uesugi-san,\\nthere's something I wanted to ask you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 105,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(As the two started talking,\\n I quickly realized it was the same thing\\n that Ichika and Itsuki mentioned earlier.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 106,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "So, you don't have any recollection, do you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 107,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Well, if that's the case,\\nthe mystery only thickens.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 108,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "For now, I'll just go look for Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 109,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(At this rate I'll have to ask Miku myself.\\n She might try to run away again,\\n but I'll chase her down if I have to.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 110,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(But, where could she have gone?\\n If I just start searching blindly,\\n I'll never be able to find her.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 111,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Where's a place Miku would likely go...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 112,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(!...\\n Got it, probably that place.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 113,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "*sigh*\\nWhy did I run away...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 114,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro is definitely mad.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 115,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Truth be told, I actually really wanted to tour around with him.\\nTo make memories, just the two of us,\\ntogether in Okinawa...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 116,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 117,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "F-Futaro?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 118,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "This place has a Japanese style to it.\\nWell, it's called the 'shoin,'\\nso I guess it's only natural.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 119,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 120,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(She's edging away from me, but at least\\n she's not running away.\\n I'll try to keep the conversation going!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 121,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You're here, I knew it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 122,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "'You knew it?' What do you mean?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 123,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I don't know how to explain it...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 124,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But, I knew you liked Japanese-style architecture, Miku.\\nSo I figured you'd be here in the 'okushoin.'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 125,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "...Is that so.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 126,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro...you know me well.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 127,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I-I guess so.\\nI mean... I am, dating you, so...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 128,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 129,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I-I'm gonna go check out other things!\\nSee ya!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 130,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ah, hey, Miku?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 131,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 132,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 133,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Man, the weather sure is nice.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 134,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yeah.\\nIt's great.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 135,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Everyone's still not back.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 136,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yeah.\\nTrue.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 137,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ahhh...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 138,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 139,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(I can't keep the conversation going!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 140,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(It's not like this kind of silence is uncommon between us.\\n Even when we go out together,\\n there are moments, we don't converse at all.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 141,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Usually, I think it's okay.\\n It's just how we are as a couple.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 142,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(But this time, it's different!\\n We've never had this much of an awkward silence before?!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 143,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Th-that's right, Miku!\\nDo you know the story about Shurijo Castle?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 144,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Remember the first gate, Shureimon we passed through?\\nIt's on the 2,000 yen bill!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 145,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Th-the 2,000 yen bill.\\nI, see.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 146,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 147,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 148,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "A-and!\\nThis plaza is called the 'una,'\\nand the ground is striped with red and white, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 149,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It was used as a marker to line up in order of rank for government officials\\nduring ceremonies!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 150,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I, see.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 151,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 152,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 153,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(...It's no use.\\n No matter what I say, Miku's not really reacting.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 154,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You're not interested in this stuff, eh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 155,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Huh?\\nThat's, not really the case.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 156,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I-I see.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 157,
      "personagem": "Both",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Miku%p-2;――\\n%p;Um, Futaro%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 158,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Sorry about the boring trivia questions.\\nIt was like studying. I'm sure it wasn't interesting.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 159,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Huh? That's not really true.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 160,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "You're interesting, you know, Futaro?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 161,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Nah, I didn't mean me, but the trivia questions.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 162,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "AH?!\\nThose were interesting, too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 163,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I-I see.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 164,
      "personagem": "Both",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Miku%p-2;――\\n%p;Um, Futaro%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 165,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Do you have any questions?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 166,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Questions?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 167,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Whether it's about Shurijo Castle, Okinawa,\\nor anything else, it doesn't matter.\\nIt could be about anything, I'd just like to talk to you Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 168,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Since we came to Okinawa,\\nwe haven't really had a chance to talk, have we?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 169,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Y-yeah.\\nThat's...right.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 170,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "You were concerned about me, weren't you?\\nYou're really kind after all, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 171,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh? What do you mean?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 172,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "No.\\nI also wanted to talk to you more, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 173,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I-is that so!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 174,
      "personagem": "Both",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Miku%p-2;――\\n%p;Um, Futaro%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 175,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hm, what?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 176,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "You go first.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 177,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Oh, really? Well, then, I was thinking tonight%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 178,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Tonight!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 179,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, if you're okay, we could go together to%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 180,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "T-together?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 181,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I-I'm gonna go take a look at that.\\nSee you later.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 182,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 183,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(I don't understand.\\n I don't have the slightest clue, what Miku is thinking.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 184,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(It's certain that she's avoiding me,\\n but it doesn't feel like she dislikes me either.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 185,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 186,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(There's no time to hesitate.\\n Let's try to get some information out of the others.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 187,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(They'd asked me what's going on earlier,\\n but maybe they actually know something?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 188,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Besides, there's a possibility\\n that I'm not the reason for Miku's strange behavior%p-2;――%p;)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 189,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 190,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(GAAAAHH! What's this uneasy feeling?!\\n I don't like it!!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 191,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "*sigh*",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 192,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(So this...is how it feels like to be the pursuer in the relationship?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 193,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Indeed, if you don't go all out,\\nnothing good will come out of it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}